{"word":"G3886 - παραλύω - paralýō - par-al-oo'-o - Feeble","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παραλύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">paralýō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">par-al-oo'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Feeble</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - திமிர்வாதகாரனாயிரு"},{"paragraph":"தளர்ந்த - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"to loose on one side or from the side"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3844 - παρά - pará - par-ah'/3844\">G3844</a> and <a href=\"#/G3089 - λύω - lýō - loo'-o/3089\">G3089</a>; to <i>loosen beside</i>, that is, <i>relax</i> (perfect passive participle <i>paralyzed</i> or <i>enfeebled</i>): - feeble, sick of the (taken with) palsy.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}